title: Setora Takaboeva
text:
Setora Takaboeva (Uzbek: Sitora Taqaboyeva; born 8 August 2001) is an Uzbekistani footballer who plays as a midfielder for Women's Championship club Sogdiana and the Uzbekistan women's national team.


== International career ==
Takaboeva capped for Uzbekistan at senior level in September 2019, during a 1–1 friendly draw against India and the Hope Cup.
